        "subject": "LU-18756 mdt: check resource IDs before init_ucred in getxattr",
        "message": "LU-18756 mdt: check resource IDs before init_ucred in getxattr\n\nWhen getting xattr on the MDT, \"mdt_check_resource_ids()\" should be\ncalled before \"mdt_init_ucred()\" to avoid acquiring identity cache\nentries for requests that will be rejected, and it ensures the\nidentity cache entries are correctly cleaned-up.\n\nFixes: 719f6763fe (\"LU-18756 sec: add resource id check to oss and mds\")\nTest-Parameters: trivial testlist=sanity-sec\nSigned-off-by: Marc Vef <mvef@whamcloud.com>\nChange-Id: I1c3168cc41caf4c00852223d7c4263d54850a3c9\nReviewed-on: https://review.whamcloud.com/c/fs/lustre-release/+/62113\nReviewed-by: Sebastien Buisson <sbuisson@ddn.com>\nReviewed-by: Andreas Dilger <adilger@dilger.ca>\nTested-by: Maloo <maloo@whamcloud.com>\nReviewed-by: Oleg Drokin <green@whamcloud.com>\nTested-by: jenkins <devops@whamcloud.com>\n"
